# Google OAuth 2.0 Web Client ID
# You can obtain this by creating a Web application client ID in Google Cloud Platform Console (https://console.cloud.google.com)
# Make sure to whitelist your local development URI (http://localhost:5173) and production domains in the authorized JavaScript origins.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-oauth-client-id-here.apps.googleusercontent.com
